title: Premier League & EFL Cup final team of the week - Football
text:
Previous slide Next slide 1 of 13 View All Skip Ad 
A team top-heavy with number nines this week and it would certainly be a problem to shoe-horn the trio into one team especially as everyone knows that Zlatan Ibrahimovic will not cede that central ground. 
But it is impossible to ignore the contributions of Manolo Gabbiadini, also in the EFL Cup Final of course, and Harry Kane who has the extraordinary ability to bounce back after adversity and struck a hat-trick just days after suffering the disappointment of an own goal and going out of the Europa League. 
Jason Burt picks his team of the weekend. EPA/Getty Images/Rex Features
